## ðŸ”§ Manual vs Automated VM Creation

**Scenario:**  
- Customer A needs 100 VMs  
- Customer B needs another 100 VMs  

Doing this **manually** through UI or shell scripts could take **100+ hours**.

> ðŸš€ A DevOps engineer uses **automation scripts** to dynamically spin up VMs with minimal effort, ensuring efficiency, consistency, and scalability.

